{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"handleOpenURL:"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","text":"NSURL"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"url"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL to process.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"url"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise."}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Test device registration","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Register device for push testing via QR code"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep link tracking"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handleOpenURL:":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"title":"handleOpenURL:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"}}}